summary: "It is an honour to be part of this legacy!" Brie Larson on Captain Marvel
title: "It is an honour to be part of this legacy!" Brie Larson on Captain Marvel
body:
“It is an honour to be part of this legacy!” #BrieLarson on #CaptainMarvel #MarvelStudios #MarvelCinematicUniverse #SamuelLJackson #BenMendelsohn #AnnetteBening #ClarkGregg #JudeLaw

Marvel Studios’ presents “Captain Marvel,” an all-new adventure from a previously unseen period in the history of the Marvel Cinematic Universe that introduces the MCU’s first stand-alone, female-franchise title character Carol Danvers aka Captain Marvel.

Acknowledged as Marvel’s mightiest Super Hero, Captain Marvel is touted to begin 2019 with a bang and is undoubtedly one of the most awaited…
